id: zw_cc_basiccontroller
label: Basic Command Class Control
category: Z-Wave|Command Classes
description: >
  Basic Command Class allows a controlling device to operate
  the primary functionality of another device without any further knowledge.
  Basic Command Class ensures a basic interoperability if no other Command Class
  is shared by two devices.

  Basic Controller component provides control of other devices using Basic Command Class.

package: Z-Wave
quality: production
source:
  - path: protocol/z-wave/ZAF/CommandClasses/Basic/src/CC_BasicController.c
include:
  - path: protocol/z-wave/ZAF/CommandClasses/Basic/inc/
    file_list:
    - path: CC_Basic.h
provides:
  - name: zw_cc_basiccontroller
